title: RL Stine - Give Yourself Goosebumps #1 to #22
description:
All books are retail ePubs. In these ebook versions, each "Turn to page..." instruction is a direct link to that page, so you tap your way through rather than flip.

#01 - Escape from the Carnival of Horrors (July 1995)
#02 - Tick Tock, You're Dead! (November 1995)
#03 - Trapped in Bat Wing Hall (December 1995)
#04 - The Deadly Experiments of Dr. Eeek (February 1996)
#05 - Night in Werewolf Woods (April 1996)
#06 - Beware of the Purple Peanut Butter (June 1996)
#07 - Under the Magician's Spell (July 1996)
#08 - The Curse of the Creeping Coffin (August 1996)
#09 - The Knight in Screaming Armor (September 1996)
#10 - Diary of a Mad Mummy (October 1996)
#11 - Deep in the Jungle of Doom (November 1996)
#12 - Welcome to the Wicked Wax Museum (December 1996)
#13 - Scream of the Evil Genie (January 1997)
#14 - The Creepy Creations of Professor Shock (February 1997)
#15 - Please Don't Feed the Vampire! (March 1997)
#16 - Secret Agent Grandma (April 1997)
#17 - Little Comic Shop of Horrors (May 1997)
#18 - Attack of the Beastly Babysitter (June 1997)
#19 - Escape from Camp Run-For-Your-Life (July 1997)
#20 - Toy Terror: Batteries Included (August 1997)
#21 - The Twisted Tale of Tiki Island (September 1997)
#22 - Return to the Carnival of Horrors (October 1997)
